    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，packet-beta类型很适合展示位级结构。我先确认一下字段顺序：前32位是端口信息，Source Port和Destination Port各占16位，对吗？",
