      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，然后是Length和Checksum各16位。关键是最后的Data字段，我们要特别标注这是承载Security_OAuth2令牌的数据区，占用32位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Length",
