    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我来构建这个结构。0-15位放Source Port，16-31位是Destination Port，32-47位Length，48-63位Checksum，最后64-95位标注为Data (Security_OAuth2)。标题也设置好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "packet-beta",
        "Source Port",
